Package com.mycompany.controller

This package is a controller and it has class with servlets.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddNewStationFormServlet
    This servlet is responsible for show form to add new station.
    AddNewStationServlet
    This servlet is responsible for handle data from user and create a new station adding it to base.
    ChooseTownServlet
    This servlet is responsible for giving to user possibility to choose station which user want to change.
    LoginPageServlet
    This servlet is responsible for hanlde log in users to this program.
    ShowStationServlet
    This servlet is responsible for show to user list with all station which exist in base.
    StartPageServlet
    This servlet is responsible for start page
    UpdateDataFormServlet
    This servlet is responsible for show to user form for to change data in chosen station
    UpdateDataServlet
    This servlet is responsible for handle data from user and update choosen station by user
